revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yaugers}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yauger'' is the 32438<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 709 individuals. ''Yauger'' is most common among White (95.49%) individuals.
